r f BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV30-C     04-27 0596
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: THE GOVERNMENT'S MICROSOFT STUMBLE
 &HT;    Moving in the (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, April 30.
