</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS -- The Amistad, a full-size reproduction of
the 129-foot slave ship, was launched recently in Mystic, Conn.,
and will make a series of calls along the East Coast on its maiden
voyage in July. Also, other briefs. (N.Y. Times News Service)
</P>
