   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   WAR-WIDOWS _ An organization of war widows called ``Regret to
Inform'' launches a new web site that its leaders see as a way to
help widows of wars to ease their pain. Many Atlanta women,
including several Vietnamese, are posting remembrances on the site,
called Widows of War. (Hendrick, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) WITH
PHOTO
