   HAPPY RENOVATION _ Many home owners manage to live through Home
Improvement Hell and tell about it. They explain how they protected
themselves, how they formed a relationship with their contractor
and, in the end, how they got exactly what they wanted. Home
renovation doesn't have to be nightmare experience. (Flanders,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
