Grade: C- (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   TV-FIXES _ Five shows that once were good and how to fix them.
(Thompson, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   SWEEPS _Wrapup of weekend viewing on the first weekend of May
sweeps, with commentary and minireviews of ``Arabian Nights'' on
ABC and ``The John Denver Story'' on CBS. (Kloer, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
