</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ELIAN-COSTS _ WASHINGTON _ After five months of around-the-clock
police protection, some riot control and transportation costs, just
what has been the cost of the Elian Gonzalez case to U.S.
taxpayers? We take a look. Developing. (Malone, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   Moving in both International/Washington categories.
</P>
<P>
   IRS-GAO _ WASHINGTON _ More than two years after a Senate
hearing aired sensational charges of abuses by the Internal Revenue
Service, a congressional report says the most serious charges could
not be corroborated. The findings were somewhat embarrassing for
some Senate Republicans, who nevertheless emphsized that the agency
did have problems. (Malone, Cox News Service)
</P>
