Heather Graham and Casey Affleck. Reviewed by A.O. Scott.
</P>
<P>
   FLINTSTONES-MOVIE-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``The Flintstones in Viva
Rock Vegas,'' starring Mark Addy and Stephen Baldwin. Reviewed by
Lawrence Van Gelder.
