failure. He was 66. A generous benefactor of the Metropolitan Opera
and Museum of Modern Art in New York and the Santa Fe Opera, Tobin
also was a major contributor to the McNay Art Museum in San
Antonio. By CARMINA DANINI and NICOLE FOY. (Already filed.)
