<HEADLINE>
MICROSOFT DOUBLES SHARE OPTIONS TO STEM STAFF EXODUS    
</HEADLINE>
   (This 400-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)     
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)     
