<P>
   CATALINA ISLAND &QL;
</P>
<P>
   AVALON, Calif. _ Catalina is often considered just a place for a
day trip from Los Angeles. But actually, the island's charms are
much more apparent when you take the time to spend a night or two
there, away from the throngs of day-tripping tourists. By BILL
HANNA. Story has moved in ``t'' travel category. &QL; 
