Lawrenceville, Ga., and were surprised to find a $3,500 lien on
their house. It turns out the homeowners assoc. whacked 'em for
having a pair of pink flamingos in their front yard and has been
fining 'em on a daily basis. (Stanford, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
