University's best known professors will make his farewell at 11
a.m. Thursday in Cannon Chapel. Archbishop Desmond Tutu is going
back to South Africa after two years on the Emory faculty. To honor
him, students will sing a South African hymn and give him a gift.
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
