<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-27 19:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9122 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-ELIMINATE-RUSSIA-CHEC     04-27 0033
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-RUSSIA-CHECHNYA-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-CHECHNYA (New York) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, April 27.
</P>
